 Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/Ni%E1%BB%87m-n%C3%B4-ki%E1%BB%81u/poem-Apyex3TmF_rPxiy1ojJ2tg">Niệm nô kiều - 念奴嬌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/author-og0yg1YWgltsRxS7PoXrcQ">Lâm Hồng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/S%E1%BA%A7u-t%E1%BB%A7i/poem-VtJE06QHWr3mXfYUO3eSFA">Sầu tủi - 悲懼</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/author-5S8czaSOqXhHlNE7NtKr8g">Đặng Trần Côn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-th%E1%BA%ADp-b%C3%A1t-Ph%E1%BA%A7n/poem-iNvJ6tBHRWQrfqVP1mxB_Q">Tặng Trịnh thập bát Phần - 贈鄭十八賁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/Thang-b%C3%A0n-ph%C3%BA/poem-zRWhSi8OLsCDGbk659PgVA">Thang bàn phú - 湯盤賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/author-kBTBt5Mbi6PPrH2sJkQAPw">Khuyết danh Việt Nam</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Ngao/poem-w_OMVHVuiVnLMUqZGoDfZg">Thượng Ngao - 上嶅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
